[size=3][b][color=#ff7700]DESCRIPTION[/color][/b]
This mod adds a female preset for Imperial race.
[b]
[color=#ff7700]REQUIREMENTS[/color][/b]
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fskse.silverlock.org%2F&t=MWQ3ZGE1MTQ1OTA3OWY2NDg4YzBiMTQ5NTczOTNmZTRiYTM1ZDUxNix3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]Skyrim Script Extender (SKSE)[/url] 
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fsharedfiles%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D8122&t=NDI3N2U4Mjc2ZWQyZWMzNjZmNTZmYWJjZjZjM2YyOTc4OWY3NzFhZSx3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]SkyUI[/url]
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F29624%2F&t=MDMxMGVlMzU3ODU2NzY1OTNkN2RlNTE3OTYxMThkNDdjMTdhOTExNSx3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]RaceMenu Mod[/url]
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F33526%2F%3F&t=ZTYzMjJmY2RlMzE1NGMzNzhlMDM2OTQyZTE2MmQ4NzFiM2U3M2RhYix3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer[/url]
[b]
[color=#ff7700]CHARACTER SPECIFIC MODS[/color][/b]
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F68311%2F&t=YzMwOTY5YmM4ZWFiOGMxZWQxZTY1MDNhMzEzNmExY2JjMzBmZjg0Yyx3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url] 
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F51602%2F&t=ZjNlNmU4NWM0OWUzOWNkZjdjNWRhNzI4N2UyMWQwMmMwN2Y0YWEwNix3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] 
[b][color=#ff7700]
ENB USED IN SCREENSHOTS[/color][/b]
[url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F50483%2F&t=MzFmZTk3NTBlYzY1ZTExZjkyMjJjYjJkZmRiMDcwZTZkMDk2ZmY2ZSx3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]Photoreal ENB - Performance[/url] 
[b]
[color=#ff7700]SETUP[/color][/b]
-Place [u]Saga.jslot[/u] at: [i]data\skse\plugins\chargen\presets[/i]
alternatively it may be: [i]\Mod Organizer\overwrite\skse\plugins\CharGen[/i]
-In game, open console [b][~][/b] and type [i]showracemenu[/i] and tap [b][Enter][/b]  
-Select imperial race and female gender
-Open Presets tab (top-right corner) in race menu
-Load Preset [b][F9][/b] click [u]Saga.jslot[/u] and open it
-If you are done, hit [b][R][/b] and name your character
[b]
[color=#ff7700]CREDITS
[/color][/b][url=http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F29624%2F&t=MDMxMGVlMzU3ODU2NzY1OTNkN2RlNTE3OTYxMThkNDdjMTdhOTExNSx3MG5BWEdYaw%3D%3D]RaceMenu Mod[/url] by [b]Expired [/b]
